---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Notes & Essays
description: Essays, study notes, and fragments, in Chinese and English.
bodyClass: essays-index
---
<section class="wrap--narrow page-intro page-intro--warm">
  <p class="eyebrow">Notes &amp; Essays</p>
  <h1 class="page__title page__title--serif">The notebook.</h1>
  <p class="page__lede">
    Slower writing, away from code. Argumentative essays, study notes, and small
    fragments, mostly in <span class="lang-zh">中文</span>, sometimes in English.
    This is where I try to think clearly about things that don't compile.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="wrap--narrow">
  <h2 class="stream-head">Essays &amp; Notes</h2>
  <ol class="essay-list">
    {% for essay in collections.essays %}
      <li class="essay-list__item lang-{{ essay.data.lang }}">
        <a href="{{ essay.url }}">
          <h3 class="essay-list__title">{{ essay.data.title }}</h3>
          {% if essay.data.lede %}<p class="essay-list__lede">{{ essay.data.lede }}</p>{% endif %}
          <time class="essay-list__date" datetime="{{ essay.date | isoDate }}">{{ essay.date | readableDate(essay.data.lang) }}</time>
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ol>
</section>

<section class="wrap--narrow">
  <h2 class="stream-head">Fragments</h2>
  <ul class="fragment-list">
    {% for f in fragments %}
      <li class="fragment lang-{{ f.lang }}">
        <p class="fragment__text">{{ f.text }}</p>
        <time class="fragment__date" datetime="{{ f.date }}">{{ f.date }}</time>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>
